citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00 p.m. on
07-Sep-16. No responsible adult was available again at 4:07 p.m. on the 07-Sep-2016. I called the phone number
provided and knocked on the residence door both times. I waited 30 minutes and hook my vehicle horn both times
too.
This attempted will be sent by regular mail.
